  <tr><td colspan="3" bgcolor="#4A2A12">One - its just a reccomended skill level, not a requirement. This helm is pretty decent, and especially so because it is tradeable. The reccomended skill level is to discourage giving this item to any 2-bit n00b.<br />
<br />
And about the size - magic armor magically resizes to fit the wearer, thats why it can be worn by any race typically. Non-magic armor (bronze, regular plate etc.) is sized, small, medium, or large.<br><br></td></tr>
